                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1417" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN DREW</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> There were greasy marks on his coat, exactly on the spot where I saw him put the bacon—I was not above three yards from him when he took it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
